Day 18 - Manga 406*
I hope that everyone learned something today. Get Good or you will end sucking dick with your best friend in an alley. Also, when the princess appeared once again, all that I could think of was that she hadn't been feed. She looks like an African kid. 
And about the second part, at some parts he looks like a small sized shit and at others like a normal sized shit so I didn't understand shit.
1/10.
Idk, I feel like I'd get it if I knew what I was reading, but otherwise it just made me feel disgusted, good art though 3/10
First 100 pages were kinda disturbing but after that it's pretty good 7/10
